ExploreFact.Text: This planet seems to be a kind of giant sponge with trees. The water levels are in a constant cycle of rising and falling.

RumorFact.Text: The Nomai kept records of Tidal Grove in an obscure location in the bottom floor of a building somewhere near the Gravity Cannon on Brittle Hollow.

ExploreFact.Text: The South Pole of this planet was apparently the breeding grounds for a local species of fish.
The North Pole of this planet has a Nomai scroll wall, and gravity crystals. A trail of gravity crystals leads up a tree.
This planet once harbored a species of fish, according to the Nomai.
The local fish evidently had five eyes, one more than everybody from Timber Hearth.
